{"tid":1958674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載分享] 用呢招協助翻牆小粉紅返去用內聯網！","createTime":"2020-04-04T21:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T19:26:51.000Z","uid":233307,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8990d3cd800765fa770dd17b506348a9aa2c13","tid":1958674,"uid":233307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T21:47:33.000Z","msg":"轉載來源：<a href=\"https://hugo3c.tw/archives/8585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhugo3c.tw%2Farchives%2F8585&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=79d8c05c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hugo3c.tw/archives/8585</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCDTUMQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCDTUMQ.png&h=64e06c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n常常在臉書、YouTube 上看到各種從大陸翻牆過來的網友，發表各種侵略性的言論嗎？現在有方法可以「回敬」他們了，而且是 100% 合法的方式，利用中國的中央網信辦 (國家互聯網信息辦公室)，檢舉違法利用 VPN 等翻牆軟體過來的民眾，將留言截圖 (越多越好)，就可以請這些網民「回家」吃自己啦！ <br />\n<br />\n第一步:<br />\n去 <a href=\"http://www.12377.cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.12377.cn%2F&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD6VNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=1415d514\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.12377.cn/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二步:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iGzG3H8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiGzG3H8.png&h=4bfeee49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點擊「違法和不良信息舉報入口」 。<br />\n<br />\n第三步:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvSp1vb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnvSp1vb.png&h=56f5eba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滑到最下面有個同意需要按一下才能繼續下一步。<br />\n<br />\n第四步:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQfGjg4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQfGjg4.png&h=fd06bdd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 點擊舉報分類選擇「其它」類。<br />\n<br />\n第五步:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p0isZhA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp0isZhA.png&h=bbb47789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點擊「匿名用戶舉報」，舉報平台選擇「客戶端 APP」，將 APP 名稱打上，並將 APP 官方的網址也貼上，最後舉報內容填寫違反使用 VPN 等類似陳述即可，因為最重要的截圖，有越多截圖越好，點擊「請選擇附件」來上傳，最後輸入驗證碼後按下繼續舉報即可。另外，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同樣重要的是，請將繁體字通通都轉成簡體字</span></strong>，舉報成功後會收到一組查詢碼。<br />\n<br />\n第六步:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnykzRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnykzRy.png&h=6f906418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n查詢舉報處理進度！看看他何時收皮"},{"pid":"aeddabbbf73607ee3f4dd063f2842ffe11434bdb","tid":1958674,"uid":233307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T23:00:03.000Z","msg":"自推x1 想多啲人知"},{"pid":"34d31d8fef8e401627807196c8b5592f7550bca7","tid":1958674,"uid":316979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T23:28:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好似幾好玩咁樣"},{"pid":"8293980278b45c0c69ebdbd6b1ff4ac9871791ab","tid":1958674,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T00:44:39.000Z","msg":"出面好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416a21c5efe54d38aa77eecb2e4e5650f1d5ba67","tid":1958674,"uid":233307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeddabbbf73607ee3f4dd063f2842ffe11434bdb","tid":1958674,"uid":233307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T23:00:03.000Z","msg":"自推x1 想多啲人知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"再推 !  多啲人知幫手淨化互聯網"},{"pid":"f0bf475a5447142b3f82d80b6a44184827d74114","tid":1958674,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:02:42.000Z","msg":"正呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d29cd4a0dccd5ec4980792d5b18eacf4043a30f","tid":1958674,"uid":233307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T08:18:18.000Z","msg":"自推x3！！！ 真係無人覺得有用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766795d7ec446559129f8dc383408a2f4c2f52f4","tid":1958674,"uid":